## 🔍 Observability (Langfuse)

This SDK supports **optional observability via Langfuse**.

Telemetry is:

-   disabled by default
-   enabled explicitly in code
-   configured via environment variables
-   safe to omit in air-gapped environments

### Install

``` bash
pip install d61864-genai[observability]
```

### Configure

Set environment variables:

``` bash
export LANGFUSE_HOST="https://langfuse.internal.scb"
export LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY="..."
export LANGFUSE_SECRET_KEY="..."
```

### Enable in Code

``` python
from d61864_genai.observability import init_telemetry

init_telemetry(service_name="claims-assistant")
```

### What Is Traced

-   LLM calls
-   embedding requests
-   retry attempts
-   errors
-   latency

