## 📐 Versioning & Compatibility

This project follows **semantic versioning**:

-   MAJOR --- breaking API changes
-   MINOR --- backward-compatible features
-   PATCH --- bug fixes

Only top-level imports are considered stable:

``` python
import d61864_genai
```

Internal module paths may change without notice.

